<C>__{laura}
<D>__{done. well. that's most of it. 9 out of 10. i told em to tell tug it was his. told her it would soften him up. she said she wished she could keep it, but she didn't love the father. i was going to drive her down the next day, we'd found a doctor. most wouldn't. she was starting to show. 3 months. you know whose kid that makes it, or have you known all along?}
<A>__{slowly, steadily, she straightens up. her figure takes back some dignity. she steps towards him deliberately. closer. right up against him. she brings her head to his, puts her lips to his ear, breathes warm breath, and says two words. the first is}
